{"tid":160443,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[1Q題] 同蟻同象有關","createTime":"2017-03-17T16:55:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-18T02:25:36.000Z","uid":9607,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cb75b93db5ddb91a108283890284ba3a00da87d1","tid":160443,"uid":9607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T16:55:03.000Z","msg":"從前有隻象<br />\n佢睇到前面有好多紅蟻<br />\n咁佢都有睇連登，知道蟻多摟死象嘅真理<br />\n於是行第二條路<br />\n點知佢又見到前面好多黑蟻<br />\n唯有再行第三條路<br />\n今次仲慘，前面有前所未見過咁多嘅白蟻<br />\n佢真係好趕時間，照行<br />\n竟然乜事都冇<br />\n<br />\n點解？"},{"pid":"5dac9e99a87ae71a4a55801ca9bee31c131618b9","tid":160443,"uid":86488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T16:56:39.000Z","msg":"因為佢有粗腳<br />\n而咁樣係好錯既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a26ac0eb269e203542be3ce078e403d56913bc09","tid":160443,"uid":9607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T17:03:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為佢有粗腳<br />\n而咁樣係好錯既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但可能有人喜歡重口味，佢哋覺得唔錯"},{"pid":"20505c78e5a5d5bac153b589e45c8859cfa694de","tid":160443,"uid":23974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T17:09:29.000Z","msg":"因為啲蟻冇嬲佢"},{"pid":"944e29601f251eb793e634362539f4911ddbb2df","tid":160443,"uid":9607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T17:27:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為啲蟻冇嬲佢</blockquote><br />\n連登嚟計一定會蟻多摟死象"},{"pid":"c3ba1d3a017355d87865d2f56857173c66cf130a","tid":160443,"uid":9607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T02:07:51.000Z","msg":"冇啦？"},{"pid":"f4d6386a71f94f092604d1a1cd006b784635b7f1","tid":160443,"uid":66555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T02:13:30.000Z","msg":"因為大白象本身的作用係比害蟲蛀食"},{"pid":"2f2442a165308417d3e9972570da2aaf35e052ea","tid":160443,"uid":9607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T02:18:46.000Z","msg":"<block